}}</ref>，該黨遂籌辦黨團大會挑選新黨領，而林頓則於同年7月展開黨領競選活動。在2003年1月舉行的黨領選舉中，林頓在首輪投票以53.5%的得票率勝出<ref>Haight, Lana. "Layton surprises locals: Supporters 'blown away' by win over Blaikie, Nystrom; Lana Haight." ''Star - Phoenix.'' Jan 27, 2003. pg. A.1.</ref>。當時沒有國會議席的林頓委託黨領選舉中得票率第二高的比利奇（{{lang|en|Bill Blaikie}}）擔任新民主黨的下議院領袖<ref>Paraskevas, Joe. "NDP leader goes after Grits on Day One." ''Sudbury Star.'' Jan 28, 2003. pg. A.8</ref>。

林頓於[[2004年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2004年聯邦大選]]中與鄧立銘於多倫多單福選區再度交鋒，今次卻由林頓勝出，讓他首度晉身國會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/parlinfo/Files/Parliamentarian.aspx?Item=878c4a88-aa8e-4e9a-961f-3829672d4dc0&Language=E&Section=ALL |title=LAYTON, The Hon. Jack, P.C., B.A., M.A., Ph.D. |publisher=加拿大國會 |accessdate=2014-04-23 |archive-date=2015-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006000054/http://www.parl.gc.ca/ParlInfo/Files/Parliamentarian.aspx?Item=878c4a88-aa8e-4e9a-961f-3829672d4dc0&Language=E&Section=ALL |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在林頓領導下的新民主黨則在全國獲得15%選票，為16年來的新高。然而，在[[多數制|多數制]]選舉制度的影響下，新民主黨只贏取19個議席。

[[加拿大自由黨|聯邦自由黨]]在這屆大選中失去多數政府地位，只能以少數政府姿態繼續執政。到了2005年末，飽受贊助醜聞（{{lang|en|sponsorship scandal}}）困擾的自由黨支持度陸續下滑，國會下議院三個反對黨則於同年11月28日通過[[不信任動議|不信任動議]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Liberal Party Loses Vote Of Confidence In Canada|first=Clifford|last=Krauss|publisher=New York Times|date=November 29, 2005|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E04E0DB1431F93AA15752C1A9639C8B63|accessdate=2014-04-23|archive-date=2016-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109105839/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E04E0DB1431F93AA15752C1A9639C8B63|dead-url=no}}</ref>，自由黨少數政府遂告倒台，並觸發2006年聯邦大選。在這屆大選中，林頓帶領新民主黨贏取29個議席，成績較上屆進步，但仍落後奪得51席的[[魁人政團|魁人政團]]和以103席屈居官方反對黨的自由黨<ref name=2006results>{{cite news|last=Delecourt|first=Susan|title=CON124 36.5% POP VOTE LIB 103 30.1% POP VOTE BLOC 51 10.5% POP VOTE NDP 29 17.4% POP VOTE Independent 1|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/access/974828531.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jan+24%2C+2006&author=Susan+Delacourt&pub=Toronto+Star&edition=&startpage=A.01&desc=CON124+36.5%25+POP+VOTE+LIB+103+30.1%25+POP+VOTE+BLOC+51+10.5%25+POP+VOTE+NDP+29+17.4%25+POP+VOTE+Independent+1|accessdate=August 26, 2011|newspaper=The Toronto Star|date=January 24, 2006|location=Toronto|page=A1|archive-date=2012-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105043051/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/access/974828531.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Jan+24%2C+2006&author=Susan+Delacourt&pub=Toronto+Star&edition=&startpage=A.01&desc=CON124+36.5%25+POP+VOTE+LIB+103+30.1%25+POP+VOTE+BLOC+51+10.5%25+POP+VOTE+NDP+29+17.4%25+POP+VOTE+Independent+1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。林頓本人在多倫多單福選區成功連任，其妻子[[鄒至蕙|鄒至蕙]]則在[[多倫多市中心|多倫多市中心]]的[[聖三一－士巴丹拿選區|聖三一－士巴丹拿選區]]首度當選國會議員，兩人成為加拿大國會有史以來第二對夫妻檔。

他再於[[2008年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2008年聯邦大選]]中成功連任，並帶領新民主黨贏取37個議席，議席總數仍然落後於魁人政團和自由黨<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/harper-bets-the-house-wins-another-minority/article1063836/ |title=Harper bets the House, wins another minority |work=Globe and Mail |location=Canada |date=Oct 15, 2008 |accessdate=March 12, 2014 |first=Campbell |last=Clark |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203232638/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/harper-bets-the-house-wins-another-minority/article1063836/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==2011年聯邦大選==
[[File:Layton_Quebec_18042011-1.jpg|thumb]]

[[加拿大總理|總理]][[史蒂芬·哈珀|史蒂芬·哈珀]]於2011年3月26日與[[加拿大總督|總督]][[大衛·勞埃德·約翰斯頓|大衛·約翰斯頓]]會面後，總督正式解散國會<ref name="CBCwrit">{{Cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/26/cv-election-writ.html |title=Election day set for May 2 |author=CBC News |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC]] |date=26 March 2011 |accessdate=26 March 2011 |archive-date=2012-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119100013/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/26/cv-election-writ.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[2011年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2011年聯邦大選]]競選活動亦告展開。林頓較早前曾接受臀部手術，在競選期間常被問及他的健康狀況，他一直堅持自己的情況足以應付黨魁的工作<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/inside-politics-blog/2011/03/layton-opens-up-about-his-health.html Layton opens up about his health] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/inside-politics-blog/2011/03/layton-opens-up-about-his-health.html |date=20120131100500 }} ''CBC News'', March 29, 2011.</ref><ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canadavotes2011/story/2011/03/11/cv2011-party-profile-ndp.html Jack Layton: The fighter] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canadavotes2011/story/2011/03/11/cv2011-party-profile-ndp.html |date=20120625091541 }} ''CBC News'', March 25, 2011. Retrieved March 30, 2011.</ref>。

競選初期新民主黨在各項民調的支持度偏低<ref>{{cite journal|author=Richard J. Brennan National Affairs Writer|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/politics/article/972241--ndp-fortunes-falling-fast-in-latest-poll|title=NDP fortunes falling fast in latest poll|publisher=thestar.com|date=April 9, 2011|accessdate=April 25, 2011|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024031459/http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/politics/article/972241--ndp-fortunes-falling-fast-in-latest-poll|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Gloria Galloway|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/though-chips-look-down-laytons-eager-to-ante-up-for-debates/article1978060|title=Layton remains game despite polls showing he's the odd man out|publisher=The Globe and Mail|date=April 8, 2011|accessdate=April 25, 2011}}</ref>，但林頓在各場黨魁電視辯論中表現理想，新民主黨的支持度亦隨之上升。林頓亦於4月3日現身[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]][[加拿大法語頻道|法語電視頻道]]清談節目{{lang|fr|''Tout le monde en parle''}}，以口語化的[[魁北克法語|魁北克法語]]交談，大受[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]法語選民歡迎<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/layton-remains-game-despite-polls-showing-hes-the-odd-man-out/article575778/ |title=Three leaders, three accents |first=Lysiane |last=Gagnon |date=April 18, 2011 |accessdate=March 12, 2014 |publisher=The Globe and Mail |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129080502/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/layton-remains-game-despite-polls-showing-hes-the-odd-man-out/article575778/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，新民主黨在該省的支持度更超越傾向[[魁獨|魁獨]]的[[魁人政團|魁人政團]]<ref>{{cite news|author=Joanna Smith Ottawa Bureau|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/politics/article/976225|title=NDP moves into tie with Liberals: Poll|publisher=thestar.com|date=April 13, 2011|accessdate=April 18, 2011|location=Toronto|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024031522/http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/politics/article/976225|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/18/canada-politics-idUSN1822211320110418|title=Canada's NDP pushes for bigger place in election sun|publisher=Reuters|date=February 14, 2011|accessdate=April 18, 2011|first=Randall|last=Palmer|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017001756/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/18/canada-politics-idUSN1822211320110418|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canadavotes2011/story/2011/04/18/cv-election-layton-quebec-812.html|title=Layton sees growing Quebec support, targets Liberals|publisher=Cbc.ca|date=April 18, 2011|accessdate=April 18, 2011|archive-date=2013-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130417162852/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canadavotes2011/story/2011/04/18/cv-election-layton-quebec-812.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到了4月尾，新民主黨在全國的支持度超越[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]，只落後於保守黨<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/25/canada-us-politics-ekos-idCATRE73O5UR20110425|title=NDP surges to strong second place in poll|publisher=Reuters|date=April 25, 2011|accessdate=April 25, 2011|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017001756/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/25/canada-us-politics-ekos-idCATRE73O5UR20110425|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="EKOS">{{cite web|url=http://www.ekospolitics.com/wp-content/uploads/full_report_april_21_2011.pdf|title=NDP Breakout Contunues As Everyone Else Spins Wheels|accessdate=April 23, 2011|last=[[EKOS|EKOS]]|date=April 2011|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204103935/https://www.ekospolitics.com/wp-content/uploads/full_report_april_21_2011.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到了選前一星期，新民主黨和林頓本人皆成為其他政黨的攻擊目標<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/news/decision-canada/surge+dominates+talk+federal+campaign+trail/4685960/story.html|title=NDP surge dominates talk on federal campaign trail|publisher=Vancouver Sun|date=April 27, 2011|accessdate=April 27, 2011|archive-date=2020-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217135641/http://www.vancouversun.com/news/decision-canada/surge+dominates+talk+federal+campaign+trail/4685960/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2011年5月2日舉行的大選中，林頓領導下的新民主黨奪得103個議席，為該黨歷來之最，並讓該黨首度成為[[官方反對黨_(加拿大)|官方反對黨]]<ref name="CBCtimeline"/>。該黨並於魁北克省大有進帳：選前該黨在魁省只得一席（即下任黨魁[[唐民凱|唐民凱]]的議席），選後則增至全省75個議席中的59個。林頓亦成功在自己的多倫多單福選區連任，並成為[[加拿大官方反對黨主席|官方反對黨黨魁]]。

==罹患癌症及逝世==
[[File:Layton_honour_guard.jpg|thumb]]

林頓於2010年2月5日宣佈自己確診患上[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]，但其後治愈。他的父親羅伯特·林頓過去亦曾患上這種癌症，但後來亦康復。<ref name="CBCtimeline"/>

2011年7月25日，明顯消瘦的林頓召開記者會宣佈自己再度患癌，但除了指明並非前列腺癌外並沒有提及是何種癌症。他亦宣佈暫時卸下黨魁一職以全力抗癌，並推薦新民主黨黨團主席[[妮科爾·特梅爾|妮科爾·特梅爾]]出任臨時黨魁<ref name="leaderpick">{{Cite web|last=LeBlanc|first=Daniel|title=Layton picks Nycole Turmel as interim leader|work=The Globe and Mail|date=July 25, 2011|url=http://www.the globeandmail.com/news/politics/layton-picks-nycole-turmel-as-interim-leader/article2108898|accessdate=July 25, 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130711015752/http://the/|archivedate=2013年7月11日}}</ref>。林頓又表示希望在同年9月國會復會後重返議事廳，但最終仍不敵癌魔，於北美東岸夏令時間2011年8月22日清晨4時45分（UTC-4）在多倫多家中病逝，終年61歲<ref name="Globe110822"/>。

他的喪禮於2011年8月27日以[[國葬|國葬]]形式在多倫多[[萊湯遜音樂廳|萊湯遜音樂廳]]舉行，出席的包括總理哈珀、[[加拿大總督|總督]][[大衛·勞埃德·約翰斯頓|約翰斯頓]]和前總理[[保羅·馬丁|馬田]]和[[克里田|克里田]]等政治人物以及多名著名演奏家，而喪禮亦開放給約600名市民入内<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/TopStories/20110827/layton-state-funeral-toronto-110827/|title=Thousands celebrate Layton's family, political life|date=August 27, 2011|accessdate=August 27, 2011|publisher=CTV News|last=DeCoste|first=Erin|archive-date=2012-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503002344/http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/TopStories/20110827/layton-state-funeral-toronto-110827/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。反對黨黨魁的喪禮通常不在以國葬規格進行之列，但哈珀破例向林頓遺孀鄒至蕙提出此安排，並獲鄒氏接納<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/ottawa-notebook/state-funeral-for-jack-layton-to-be-held-saturday/article2138000/|title=State funeral for Jack Layton to be held Saturday|date=August 22, 2011|accessdate=August 22, 2011|publisher=''The Globe and Mail''|last=Taber|first=Jane|archive-date=2011-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111128210044/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/ottawa-notebook/state-funeral-for-jack-layton-to-be-held-saturday/article2138000/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在此之前，林頓的靈柩分別停放於[[渥太華|渥太華]][[國會山莊_(加拿大)|國會大樓]]（8月24至25日）和[[多倫多市政廳|多倫多市政廳]]（8月26至27日）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/article/1043470--jack-layton-to-lie-in-state-at-toronto-city-hall|title=Jack Layton to lie in state at Toronto City Hall|date=August 23, 2011 |accessdate=August 23, 2011 |publisher=''Toronto Star''}}</ref>，連日來有數以千計民眾前往憑弔<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/story/2011/08/26/layton-reaction.html|title=Public outpouring for Layton not surprising, experts say|date=August 26, 2011|accessdate=August 27, 2011|publisher=CBC News|last=Gollom|first=Mark|archive-date=2011-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827091435/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/story/2011/08/26/layton-reaction.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/08/26/jack-layton-toronto-repose.html|title=Thousands of Toronto mourners honour Layton|date=August 26, 2011|accessdate=August 27, 2011|publisher=CBC News|archive-date=2013-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130905202003/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/08/26/jack-layton-toronto-repose.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的遺體火化後，骨灰分別撒於家鄉魁省哈德遜鎮<ref>{{cite news |author=Jane Taber |title=Jack Layton's ashes scattered in hometown of Hudson, Que. |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/ottawa-notebook/jack-laytons-ashes-scattered-in-hometown-of-hudson-que/article617914/ |work=The Globe and Mail |location=Toronto |date=October 3, 2011 |accessdate=December 9, 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127095820/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/ottawa-notebook/jack-laytons-ashes-scattered-in-hometown-of-hudson-que/article617914/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及多倫多市的阿爾岡昆島<ref>{{cite news |author=Mitchel Raphael |title=Some of Jack Layton's ashes sprinkled on Toronto Island |url=http://www2.macleans.ca/2012/07/17/some-of-jack-laytons-ashes-sprinkled-on-toronto-island/ |work=Macleans |location=Canada |date=July 17, 2012 |accessdate=December 9, 2013 |archive-date=2014-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305131048/http://www2.macleans.ca/2012/07/17/some-of-jack-laytons-ashes-sprinkled-on-toronto-island/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和多倫多大墓園（{{lang|en|Toronto Necropolis}}）<ref>{{cite news |title=Headstone for Jack Layton unveiled |url=http://toronto.ctvnews.ca/headstone-for-jack-layton-unveiled-1.923904 |work=CTV Toronto |date=August 21, 2012 |accessdate=December 9, 2013 |archive-date=2017-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827081010/http://toronto.ctvnews.ca/headstone-for-jack-layton-unveiled-1.923904 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

